00:36.870 --> 00:37.814
Don't let 'em

00:39.660 --> 00:41.616
[Tony] I've always been rough
around the edges.

00:42.290 --> 00:43.826
Or at least that's what people think.

00:44.830 --> 00:46.366
Maybe it's what I want them to think.

00:46.790 --> 00:48.371
I hate you for making me do this.

00:48.630 --> 00:51.918
No, you don't. Admit it, you love it,
and you love me for it.

00:52.420 --> 00:54.718
