05:56.430 --> 05:57.556
And I can't tell anyone.

05:59.560 --> 06:00.970
You should tell someone.

06:02.610 --> 06:03.895
Someone who's alive.

06:08.570 --> 06:09.480
I tried to forget you.

06:11.990 --> 06:13.446
I tried so hard.

06:16.250 --> 06:17.205
