but sometimes Star Trek.

06:34.720 --> 06:37.348
Or walking me home from work,
or having lunch together.

06:37.850 --> 06:38.839
Or kissing you.

06:40.020 --> 06:41.510
I can't forget kissing you.

06:42.980 --> 06:45.312
I think maybe it was
the happiest I've ever been.

06:48.110 --> 06:49.441
For, like, 15 seconds.

06:51.860 --> 06:53.691
I'd give anything to kiss you again.

07:09.420 --> 07:10.250
