08:37.640 --> 08:38.925
Yeah, I'm fine, Dad.

08:43.180 --> 08:44.135
What is he doing here?

08:44.890 --> 08:47.267
You said he was gone.
You said he ran away.

08:47.360 --> 08:50.261
Hey, he didn't--
What are you doing? Dad.

08:50.360 --> 08:53.102
